<lb ed="I" n="0115a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>道俗九十人造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0115a00" type="honorific"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之一　碑陰</cb:mulu><head>之一　碑陰</head>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0115a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0115a0101">
<lb ed="I" n="0115a02" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0115a03" type="honorific"/>太子得道諸天送刀与太子剔
<lb ed="I" n="0115a04" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0115a05" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0115a06" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0115a07" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0115a08" type="honorific"/>定光佛入國菩□□薩花時
<lb ed="I" n="0115a09" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0115a10" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0115a11" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0115a12" type="honorific"/>
